      <Meanings>
        <Meaning id="268caf79-eafb-45ee-b75a-be064b5393c0" type="Adjective">
          <Vi>theo giờ; theo từng giờ</Vi>
          <En>occurring, paid, or done for each hour; measured or reckoned by the hour.</En>
          <Example>She earns $15 an hour, so her hourly wage is relatively low.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="c63e1878-ddf7-4d8d-872a-6b75a739cab1">
              <Vi>Mô tả mức lương được tính theo từng giờ làm việc.</Vi>
              <En>Describing a wage or salary calculated per hour of work.</En>
            </Situation>
            <Situation id="f5949b31-2a04-4171-877d-ea6d91bea48e">
              <Vi>Dùng để chỉ tần suất hoặc chu kỳ diễn ra mỗi giờ.</Vi>
              <En>Used to indicate frequency or a cycle that occurs every hour (e.g., hourly updates, hourly reports).</En>
            </Situation>
